data.description: Grove at Bull Creek offers an active lifestyle for the whole family with future community amenities that include pocket parks, walking trails, playscapes, grilling areas and more. Enjoy the charm of locally-owned shops and entertainment in Taylor's downtown district, or spend the day on the water at Granger Lake, just minutes away. New construction plans offer open-concept styles with flexible living space. Discover our consumer-inspired Life Tested floor plans today.
